osvSchema.details: Improper input validation in the BIOS firmware for some Intel(R) Processors may allow an authenticated user to potentially enable denial of service via adjacent access.

description_data.value: Improper input validation in the BIOS firmware for some Intel(R) Processors may allow an authenticated user to potentially enable denial of service via adjacent access.

descriptions.value: Improper input validation in the BIOS firmware for some Intel(R) Processors may allow an authenticated user to potentially enable denial of service via adjacent access.

La validación de entrada incorrecta en el firmware del BIOS para Intel(R) Processors puede permitir que un usuario autenticado potencialmente habilite la denegación de servicio a través del acceso adyacente.
